>> I don't have a lot of
memories of the first couple

00:00:13.120 --> 00:00:15.220 align:middle line:90%
of years of my life.

00:00:15.220 --> 00:00:19.870 align:middle line:84%
And I know that we lived
in a house in Glendale

00:00:19.870 --> 00:00:21.040 align:middle line:90%
when I was born.

00:00:21.040 --> 00:00:24.880 align:middle line:84%
I know we moved from that house
to a much larger house in North

00:00:24.880 --> 00:00:27.890 align:middle line:90%
Hollywood when I was three.

00:00:27.890 --> 00:00:32.229 align:middle line:84%
And most of my early
memories are from that house.

00:00:32.229 --> 00:00:34.060 align:middle line:90%
And that was a very nice house.

00:00:34.060 --> 00:00:38.140 align:middle line:84%
So already, by the time my
earliest memories are there,

00:00:38.140 --> 00:00:42.460 align:middle line:84%
