00:00:47.395 --> 00:00:49.840 align:middle line:84%
But my dad was pretty
good at what he did.

00:00:49.840 --> 00:00:55.160 align:middle line:84%
And he did make money
starting pretty quickly.

00:00:55.160 --> 00:01:01.720 align:middle line:84%
